name: project_short_name
description: TCGA project abbreviation, eg TCGA-BRCA (ISB-CGC added column)

name: case_barcode
description: TCGA case barcode, eg TCGA-AP-A1DV (ISB-CGC added column)

name: sample_barcode
description: TCGA sample barcode, eg TCGA-AP-A1DV-01A (ISB-CGC added column)

name: aliquot_barcode
description: TCGA aliquot barcode, eg TCGA-AP-A1DV-10A-01D-A135-09 (ISB-CGC added column)

name: chromosome
description: From the GDC file isoform_coords column, parsed second field

name: start_pos
description: From the GDC file isoform_coords column, parsed third field

name: end_pos
description: From the GDC file isoform_coords column, parsed third field

name: strand
description: From the GDC file isoform_coords column, parsed fourth field

name: mirna_transcript
description: From the GDC file miRNA_region column, parsed first field

name: mirna_accession
description: From the GDC file miRNA_region column, parsed second field, if present

name: fileUUID
description: GDC identifier for file with this data (ISB-CGC added column)
